' @id(DOM-SESSION-CONTEXT)
' @desc(DOM-SESSION-CONTEXT, "The briefing payload Project::session_context() returns and `mdd context` prints: a whole-map table of contents (one TocEntry per concept kind -> count of concepts and @ids, derived from .mdd/map) plus a freshness verdict mirrored from MapStatusReport (the fresh flag and drift list). Implemented as a SessionContext struct in mdd-core.")
' @id(DOM-MAP-BASELINE)
' @desc(DOM-MAP-BASELINE, "The freshness baseline map_status diffs from. Resolution rule (cycle 0014): an explicit source_revision in .mdd/map/manifest.yml wins; when absent, derive it from git as the last commit that touched the current-side diagrams, reusing the existing git+syn changed_code engine. No stored field is required and nothing is written to .git. Resolves to absent only when there is no git history yet (-> FRESH, no baseline).")
' @id(DOM-SESSION-HOOK)
' @desc(DOM-SESSION-HOOK, "The mdd-managed Claude Code SessionStart hook entry that mdd init merges into .claude/settings.json: type=command, command=`mdd context`. The merge is idempotent and keyed by command so re-init never duplicates it; mdd clean removes exactly this entry and leaves any user-authored hooks untouched.")
' Objective domain model for agent session bootstrap (cycle 0014).
title Agent session bootstrap — domain (objective)

class SessionContext <<value>> <<missing>> {
  + toc : TocEntry[]
  + fresh : boolean
  + drift : MapDrift[]
}

class TocEntry <<value>> {
  + kind : ModelKind
  + concept_count : int
  + id_count : int
}

class MapBaseline <<value>> {
  + explicit : Revision [0..1]
  + resolve() : Revision [0..1]
}

class SessionHook <<value>> {
  + event : "SessionStart"
  + type : "command"
  + command : "mdd context"
}

SessionContext "1" o-- "*" TocEntry
SessionContext ..> MapBaseline : freshness via map_status

note right of MapBaseline
  resolve(): the explicit source_revision when set,
  otherwise the last commit touching the current
  diagrams (git log over .mdd/models/current).
  Absent only when no git history exists.
end note

note bottom of SessionHook
  Merged into .claude/settings.json by mdd init;
  removed by mdd clean. Idempotent, keyed by command.
end note
@enduml
